-*- texinfo -*-
@deftypefn {Mapping Function} {} arg (@var{z})
@deftypefnx {Mapping Function} {} angle (@var{z})
Compute the argument of @var{z}, defined as
@iftex
@tex
$\theta = \tan^{-1}(y/x)$.
@end tex
@end iftex
@ifinfo
@var{theta} = @code{atan (@var{y}/@var{x})}.
@end ifinfo
@noindent
in radians. 

For example,

@example
@group
arg (3 + 4i)
     @result{} 0.92730
@end group
@end example
@end deftypefn
